Introduction

TMC, short for TooManyColors, is a male duo that debuted in 2023 under MyDoll Entertainment. The duo consists of Wonsik, a former member of Apeace, and Seunghyuk.

They opened their official SNS accounts on November 29, 2022, to introduce themselves to the public.

They released their first pre-debut digital single “Color” on June 20, 2023, and announced that they will also release a Japanese version of the song on August 2.

On September 6, 2023, TMC announced that their fan club name will be TOUR, which is a combination of TMC and OUR, meaning the fans and TMC will become one and travel together in the future.
